In the 2nd year of {{jalink|Reiki|Q1373115}} (717), Hachiman Shrine was established as a subordinate shrine within the precincts<ref name="八幡神社">From the inscription on the monument marking the former site of Hachiman Shrine within the grounds of the Inaba District Gymnasium, Kakamigahara City.</ref>{{sfn|Kawashima Town|1982|p=1174}}.

