'''Shirahige Shrine''' (しろひげじんじゃ) is a {{ill|lt=Shinto shrine|Q845945|WD=Q845945|1=Shinto shrine}} located in {{ill|lt=Kawashima Kasada-chō|Q131938355|WD=Q131938355|1=Kawashima Kasada-chō}}, {{ill|lt=Kakamigahara City|Q641491|WD=Q641491|1=Kakamigahara}}, {{ill|lt=Gifu Prefecture|Q131277|WD=Q131277|1=Gifu Prefecture}} ({{ill|lt=Shirahige Shrine|Q705303|WD=Q705303|1=Shirahige Shrine}}). Under the {{ill|lt=Modern system of ranked Shinto shrines|Q712534|WD=Q712534|lt=shrine ranking system|1=Modern system of ranked Shinto shrines}}, it was formerly classified as a village shrine. It is designated a {{ill|lt=Kinpei-sha|Q119929592|WD=Q119929592|lt=Shirohei-sha|1=Kinpei-sha}} by the Gifu Prefecture Association of Shinto Shrines.

It is one of the candidate shrines (ronsa) for Kawashima Shrine of Kawashima in {{ill|lt=Haguri District|Q1032507|WD=Q1032507|1=Haguri District}}, {{ill|lt=Owari Province|Q514506|WD=Q514506|1=Owari Province}}, listed in the {{ill|lt=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|Q11064932|WD=Q11064932|lt=Engishiki|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō}} {{sfn|Kawashima Town|1982|pp=1179–1181}}<ref>The Owari-shi (a local gazetteer compiled by order of the {{ill|lt=Owari Domain|Q1062072|WD=Q1062072|1=Owari Domain}} in {{ill|lt=Tenpō|Q1369045|WD=Q1369045|1=Tenpō}} 15 ({{ill|lt=1844|Q7633|WD=Q7633|1=1844}})) records that “the Junior Third Rank Kawashima Tenjin of Haguri District listed in the Engishiki is the Shirahige Shrine of Kasada-jima Village.”</ref>. Other candidate shrines include {{ill|lt=Enoki Shrine (Kakamigahara)|Q134893091|WD=Q134893091|lt=Enoki Shrine|1=Enoki Shrine}} in {{ill|lt=Kawashima Matsukura-chō|Q131870131|WD=Q131870131|1=Kawashima Matsukura-machi}}, Kakamigahara City, and {{ill|lt=Kawashima Shrine (Kōnan)|Q11478285|WD=Q11478285|lt=Kawashima Shrine|1=Kawashima Shrine}} in Miyata-chō, {{ill|lt=Kōnan City|Q820496|WD=Q820496|1=Kōnan, Aichi}}, {{ill|lt=Aichi Prefecture|Q80434|WD=Q80434|1=Aichi Prefecture}}.

